instruction: Describe a popular game from the 1990s.
output: One of the most popular games from the 1990s was The Sims. This life simulation game allowed players to create and control virtual people in a simulated environment. Players could go about their daily lives, build relationships with other Sims, build houses, go on adventures, and even have a job. The game was a commercial and critical success, and spawned multiple sequels and spin-offs.
